NumPy ka Real Meaning

NumPy = Numerical Python

| Excel Me        | NumPy Me              |
| --------------- | --------------------- |
| Column          | Array                 |
| Row             | Index                 |
| Formula         | Vector Operation      |
| SUM(A1:A100000) | arr.sum() (100x fast) |


------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=SUM(B2:B100000)


import numpy as np

salary = np.array([25000,30000,28000,35000])
print(salary.sum())

